{"tid":108050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"提升英文既方法","createTime":"2017-02-05T02:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T04:14:37.000Z","uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61bb80a66c6a6208f81c6f51154dada732734279","tid":108050,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:15:30.000Z","msg":"想問下有咩方法（除左睇多啲書) 可以提高自己既英文水平 例如Grammar<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手諗下, 最好有人可以幫手開個group 集思廣益 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce19230417d8ced732c97ecb8b5fe0b30e9a5db","tid":108050,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:17:50.000Z","msg":"Grammar 真係要睇grammar 書<br />\n跟住你可以從 記單詞做起<br />\n睇戲唔識既字 記低<br />\n長期就記多少少同義"},{"pid":"f8b4ca358de6ecd2220e98f945e83320edd26d46","tid":108050,"uid":82186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:19:36.000Z","msg":"睇美劇"},{"pid":"cd9e39e9b6bed92eaa00f8d83743abbadb840644","tid":108050,"uid":33216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:21:03.000Z","msg":"識返個鬼妹同居"},{"pid":"3e3616c7c603c2211bed3dc94aa517434adc06b2","tid":108050,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Grammar 真係要睇grammar 書<br />\n跟住你可以從 記單詞做起<br />\n睇戲唔識既字 記低<br />\n長期就記多少少同義</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實睇戲睇電影都少有唔識既字 多數係去到睇新聞先會多唔識 但好多時候新聞用字又相對嚟講比較難 同有啲唔常用 咁既情況之下點睇呢？"},{"pid":"77eb348bbfa2250c585177a20c9e972d785adc41","tid":108050,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇美劇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇美劇最多都係spoken English, 唔會好似讀篇文出嚟"},{"pid":"0981ef34d246ff5eceeb3a3f3d16cb46541d67d7","tid":108050,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識返個鬼妹同居</blockquote><br />\n有無啲現實些少既建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3ff612451cde2eeb518aba58717c398d234da4","tid":108050,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:39:46.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"650b09768a62dbc265cb06bae0d15f324e02357b","tid":108050,"uid":73909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T02:56:50.000Z","msg":"Working holiday"},{"pid":"564cacaa74d0e1a62543357c4eac7557d8580f60","tid":108050,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:26:20.000Z","msg":"睇英美劇   勁睇一套有幾季   <br />\n甚至amazing race     幾廿季果d<br />\n<br />\n由要字幕變無字幕  自然<br />\n都聽得明<br />\n<br />\n再搭一份 老闆同客都係鬼佬既工"},{"pid":"13f859ec8e66710259f2ddb157388bb3dabe57f8","tid":108050,"uid":59287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:27:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"23736a98da51ec0d70293dee23bf6c63609d45c7","tid":108050,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇美劇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇美劇最多都係spoken English, 唔會好似讀篇文出嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀文科咪背經典   理科咪睇論文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bafd50b2fc4f192f992e135726c60d90b725ee4","tid":108050,"uid":61211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:41:32.000Z","msg":"唔急既，咪由興趣開始囉。<br />\n<br />\n我以前好鍾意魔獸世界，就由仔細讀英文任務既內文開始，之後就睇wowpedia 去了解成個魔獸宇宙既來龍去脈。由我最鍾意既不死族（天災）The Scourge 開始讀，慢慢去返泰坦創世果堆野。其間唔識既字就查，查完個字再對返前文後理去理解。慢慢讀同寫都進步，用既字都多左。<br />\n<br />\n聽同講就一開始靠睇戲開英文字幕，一樣：唔識咪停，查完再對返上文下理去消化。<br />\n<br />\n加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38315a9fb866f0352672d3ec4dce393e2efb10e","tid":108050,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔急既，咪由興趣開始囉。<br />\n<br />\n我以前好鍾意魔獸世界，就由仔細讀英文任務既內文開始，之後就睇wowpedia 去了解成個魔獸宇宙既來龍去脈。由我最鍾意既不死族（天災）The Scourge 開始讀，慢慢去返泰坦創世果堆野。其間唔識既字就查，查完個字再對返前文後理去理解。慢慢讀同寫都進步，用既字都多左。<br />\n<br />\n聽同講就一開始靠睇戲開英文字幕，一樣：唔識咪停，查完再對返上文下理去消化。<br />\n<br />\n加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前個fd全級第一 英文又流利 話打機同啲鬼佬學返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389880c8682de33785eab6e3d1ab51622dcbc696","tid":108050,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔急既，咪由興趣開始囉。<br />\n<br />\n我以前好鍾意魔獸世界，就由仔細讀英文任務既內文開始，之後就睇wowpedia 去了解成個魔獸宇宙既來龍去脈。由我最鍾意既不死族（天災）The Scourge 開始讀，慢慢去返泰坦創世果堆野。其間唔識既字就查，查完個字再對返前文後理去理解。慢慢讀同寫都進步，用既字都多左。<br />\n<br />\n聽同講就一開始靠睇戲開英文字幕，一樣：唔識咪停，查完再對返上文下理去消化。<br />\n<br />\n加油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前好鐘意打機 而家相對嚟講都打少左機 <br />\n<br />\n興趣都唔算多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9649cd92e2484750818ee8fdf6b23ebf36949462","tid":108050,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:47:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇美劇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇美劇最多都係spoken English, 唔會好似讀篇文出嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀文科咪背經典   理科咪睇論文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但唔知巴打覺唔覺經典嚟講 有啲相對用緊old English, 而家無咩人用 甚至有啲sentence structure 都好似咁"},{"pid":"ac8a4acc9887b77fca47c1674160218a6965672d","tid":108050,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇英美劇   勁睇一套有幾季   <br />\n甚至amazing race     幾廿季果d<br />\n<br />\n由要字幕變無字幕  自然<br />\n都聽得明<br />\n<br />\n再搭一份 老闆同客都係鬼佬既工</blockquote><br />\n呢啲有做 但未到返工年齡"},{"pid":"12624c0c013fb9ccc91db937e57421bfe9c98512","tid":108050,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"去d酒吧做waiter"},{"pid":"fb44f268e63bbb3d3b8ab6bdf564bcf1c6137e5c","tid":108050,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇美劇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇美劇最多都係spoken English, 唔會好似讀篇文出嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀文科咪背經典   理科咪睇論文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但唔知巴打覺唔覺經典嚟講 有啲相對用緊old English, 而家無咩人用 甚至有啲sentence structure 都好似咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要實用咪睇多D報紙專欄  同雜誌<br />\n<br />\n大學圖書館一定有最UPDATE  英文雜誌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4006d895aa1c354a7d10e65e895bbe13465291","tid":108050,"uid":12630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀文科咪背經典   理科咪睇論文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但唔知巴打覺唔覺經典嚟講 有啲相對用緊old English, 而家無咩人用 甚至有啲sentence structure 都好似咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要實用咪睇多D報紙專欄  同雜誌<br />\n<br />\n大學圖書館一定有最UPDATE  英文雜誌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有咩推介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcd364a8bdbb17a997a3a3ab83b95d1ee75c82d","tid":108050,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T04:14:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀文科咪背經典   理科咪睇論文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但唔知巴打覺唔覺經典嚟講 有啲相對用緊old English, 而家無咩人用 甚至有啲sentence structure 都好似咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要實用咪睇多D報紙專欄  同雜誌<br />\n<br />\n大學圖書館一定有最UPDATE  英文雜誌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有咩推介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n免費野  你中意睇乜咪睇乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}